    <h1>Security Guidelines</h1>
    <p>All devices, web sites, and software applications must comply with UM-System Information Security requirements.</p>
    <p>Newly created web sites, and new web products also need to successfully pass a Web Application Vulnerability scan.</p>
    <p>New purchases also require an IT Security form.</p>
    <p>Existing web sites should be periodically scanned with a Web Application Vulnerability scan, to ensure continued compliance. You can contact your campus Information Security office for assistance with these scans.</p>
    
